Subject: [PATCH] fix(release): pin real libheif 1.23.1 and automate upstream
 sync

The first libheif-v1.23.1 asset was built from vcpkg 2026.05.25 (port
1.21.2). Pin the vcpkg commit that ships 1.23.1, verify heif_version.h
before publish, omit debug/, emit SHA256 sidecars, and add a scheduled
upstream sync workflow.

Co-authored-by: FRITZ|FRITZ <fritz-fritz@users.noreply.github.com>
